In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF Stanley M. CHESLEY. No. D-2731. Supreme Court of the United States June 17, 2013. Stanley M. Chesley, of Cincinnati, Ohio, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.

No opinion found. Click here to view source material.
